                </div>
              </details>

              <details class="wm-acc" name="wm-acc">
                <summary>
                  <span class="wm-acc-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3l8 4v6c0 4.5-3.5 7-8 8-4.5-1-8-3.5-8-8V7l8-4z"/></svg>
                  </span>
                  <span class="wm-acc-title">Materiał i bezpieczeństwo</span>
                  <span class="wm-acc-chevron" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                  </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="wm-acc-body">
                  <p>Wykonana z <strong>bezpiecznego tworzywa</strong> dopuszczonego do kontaktu z żywnością.</p>
                  <ul class="wm-acc-list">
                    <li><strong>Mycie w zmywarce:</strong> tak, górny kosz, do 70°C</li>
                    <li><strong>Antypoślizgowy spód:</strong> nie ślizga się po kafelkach</li>
                    <li><strong>Kulka:</strong> trwale zamocowana, nie wypada</li>
                    <li><strong>Krawędzie:</strong> zaokrąglone, bezpieczne dla pyska</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </details>

              <details class="wm-acc" name="wm-acc">
                <summary>
                  <span class="wm-acc-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13"/><polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/></svg>
                  </span>
                  <span class="wm-acc-title">Dostawa i zwroty</span>
                  <span class="wm-acc-chevron" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                  </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="wm-acc-body">
                  <p><strong>Zamówienia do 14:00</strong> wysyłamy tego samego dnia.</p>
                  <ul class="wm-acc-list">
                    <li><strong>InPost Paczkomat:</strong> 9,99 zł · 24h</li>
                    <li><strong>Kurier InPost:</strong> 14,99 zł · 24–48h</li>
                    <li><strong>Pobranie:</strong> 19,99 zł</li>
                    <li><strong>Darmowa dostawa</strong> przy zestawie 3 sztuk</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p><strong>30 dni</strong> na bezproblemowy zwrot. Nie pytamy o powód.</p>
                </div>
              </details>
            </div>

            {!allOutOfStock && firstVariant && (
              <StickyATCBar
                client:idle
                productName={product.name}
                compactName="WolnaMiska"
                price={lowestPrice}
                variantId={firstVariant.id}
                scrollThreshold={30}
                imageUrl={mainImage ? buildAssetUrl(mainImage.preview, 'medium') : undefined}
              />
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================ -->
    <!-- CUSTOM SECTIONS — handoff Claude Design (WolnaMiska PDP) -->
    <!-- ============================================ -->
    <div class="wm-pdp">

      <!-- 02 TRUST STRIP -->
      <section class="trust-strip">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="trust-list">
            <div class="trust-item">
              <span class="trust-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 3l8 4v6c0 4.5-3.5 7-8 8-4.5-1-8-3.5-8-8V7l8-4z"/></svg></span>
              <span><strong>Bezpieczne tworzywo</strong><small>dla psa i kota</small></span>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-item">
              <span class="trust-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M4 6h16v12H4z"/><path d="M8 10v4M12 10v4M16 10v4"/></svg></span>
              <span><strong>Zmywarka 70°C</strong><small>górny kosz</small></span>
            </div>
